Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.06,0:21:32.77,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\fad(200,200)}派手な飾りも、
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.89,0:21:34.48,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\fad(200,200)}いらないから
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.69,0:21:36.52,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\fad(200,200)}食卓囲もう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.60,0:21:38.31,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\fad(200,200)}昨日のミスも
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.44,0:21:40.15,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\fad(200,200)}不安な明日も
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.28,0:21:41.32,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\fad(200,200)}添えて
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.69,0:21:43.82,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\fad(200,200)}ねぇ、いらない何も
