Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.82,0:21:47.57,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\fad(200,200)}シャレた盛り付けも、
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.66,0:21:49.28,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\fad(200,200)}いらないから
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.53,0:21:51.29,edjp,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)}{\fad(200,200)}涙の味はも
